    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Nearly complete copy of the Qurʼān, the first two folios are missing, so the text begins with verse 17 of al-Baqarah and one folio is missing from the end, so the last complete sūrah is al-Māʻūn.</subfield>
